    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Visi Media Asia Tbk operates as an integrated media convergence company in Indonesia. The company operates in two segments: Advertisement and Non-Advertisement. The company operates tvOne, a news and sports television station; ANTV that provides drama, comedy, animation, and other general entertainment programs; viva.co.id, a news portal; intipseleb.com; sahijab.com jagodangdut.com, and vlix.id sites; and vivanews.com, ANTVklik.com, and tvOnenews.com. It also provides trading, business management, consultancy services; office rental, property management, and other services; internet and website advertising services; private television broadcasting services; television broadcasting industry services; and visual communication design services. PT Visi Media Asia Tbk was founded in 2004 and is based in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT Visi Media Asia Tbk is a subsidiary of PT Bakrie Global Ventura.",
